description: This file defines the interface INoteService, which specifies the contract for note management operations such as retrieving all notes, fetching by ID, creating, updating, and deleting notes.

classes.name: INoteService
classes.description: Interface outlining the service contract for note operations in the backend.

methods.name: GetAll
methods.description: Returns all notes as an enumerable collection.

methods.name: GetById
methods.description: Retrieves a note by its GUID. Returns null if not found.

methods.name: Create
methods.description: Creates a new note and returns it.

methods.name: Update
methods.description: Updates an existing note identified by GUID, returning the updated note or null if not found.

methods.name: Delete
methods.description: Deletes a note by GUID, returning true if successful or false if not found.
